    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_chipperfield_555698",
        "quote": "Architecture has curled up in a ball and it's about itself. It has found itself either as a freakshow, where you're not sure if it's good or bad but at least it's interesting, or at the behest of forces of commerce.",
