    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_chipperfield_555703",
        "quote": "In Britain, we've tended to replace the kind of architectural culture valued in much of Europe with an in-flight magazine lifestyle - all branding, marketing and 'accessibility', a word that usually means dumbing-down.",
