    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_chipperfield_555709",
        "quote": "When the Americans are behind you, they're behind you 100%, and this gives you real confidence as an architect. They expect you to lead a building project - to make the kind of big and costly decisions that, in Britain, have been handed over to project managers and cost-cutters.",
